Nexus is dedicated to Laz Rojas, an inspirational designer who consistently came up with interesting, engaging and creative works. Through a number of interesting discussions, he also gave me insight into the history of Mac Wolfenstein and the development of the community, for which I am grateful.\
\
If you've not played Laz's scenarios, do give them a try. You won't be disappointed! Do an internet search to find his website!\
\
Sections of Nexus were inspired by the following scenarios, all by Laz, and use graphics taken from them:\
\
Hitler's Graveyard\
Astrostein\
Amerika the Beautiful\
Die, Himmler, Die!\
\
If you're wondering why I haven't ported over the sounds, this is because of the condensed nature of Nexus. Many sounds in Wolfenstein have multiple uses, so changing sounds to make one quadrant sound good would mess up the sounds in the other quadrants! In the end, I decided to stick with the original sounds, since I think these give the best experience across all four quadrants.\
